Package: dbn
Type: Package
Title: Dynamic Bilinear Network Models for Ordinal Relational Data
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-01-06
Authors@R: c(
    person("Shahryar", "Minhas", email = "minhassh@msu.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Tosin", "Salau", email = "salaubol@msu.edu",
           role = "aut")
    )
Author: Shahryar Minhas [aut, cre], Tosin Salau [aut]
Maintainer: Shahryar Minhas <minhassh@msu.edu>
Description: Implements Dynamic Bilinear Network (DBN) models for analyzing 
    temporal ordinal relational data. Provides both static and dynamic 
    variants of bilinear autoregressive models with Gaussian rank likelihood 
    for ordinal outcomes. Includes functions for model estimation via MCMC, 
    visualization, and diagnostics.
